snippet.title: No More Heroes 2: Desperate Struggle – Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Travis Touchdown has fallen all the way to #51 in the assassin rankings, and he won’t rest until he’s back on top—and  gets some revenge along the way! No More Heroes 2: Desperate Struggle is AVAILABLE NOW on Nintendo Switch! 

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/no-more-heroes-2-desperate-struggle-switch/
 
#NoMoreHeroes #NintendoSwitch
